.Dd June 24, 2026
.Dt X11DND_TARGET_GET_WINDOW 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm x11dnd_target_get_window
.Nd retrieve the target window from a drop session
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libx11dnd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In x11dnd.h
.Ft Window
.Fn x11dnd_target_get_window "X11DndTargetSession *sess"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn x11dnd_target_get_window
returns the
.Vt Window
that was registered with
.Xr x11dnd_register_target 3 .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
The target
.Vt Window .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr x11dnd_register_target 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd_source_get_window 3 ,
.Xr x11dnd 3
